divs: Sighting DetailsI WENT TO MEET MY GIRLFRAND TO GO TO LUNCH. BUT FOR I GOT TO THE BUS BENCH. I FEALT LIKE LOOKING UP. GLESS WHAT I SAW UP IN THE SKY ABOUT THE SECOND CLOUD LEVEL. DO YOU SEE THAT A LADY THAT WAS THERE FANTED SO WE WENT TO CACH HER .THAY WERE ABOUT FIVE HUNDRED FEET AWAY
